1
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:09,440
Master.

2
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:12,420
I'm looking at the amulet.

3
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,640
You are so amazing, Master.

4
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:16,280
With just a simple amulet,

5
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:17,640
you can turn an ordinary bow

6
00:02:17,640 --> 00:02:18,880
into a divine weapon.

7
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:20,760
It's not a divine weapon.

8
00:02:21,640 --> 00:02:23,100
It's an enchanted weapon.

9
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:25,570
When the magic power is exhausted,

10
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:27,540
the bow will return to normal.

11
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:36,170
Although you don't have much magic power,

12
00:02:36,480 --> 00:02:38,340
your spiritual energy is not bad.

13
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:39,960
If you practice,

14
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:42,370
even without enchantment,

15
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:44,970
you can master some spells.

16
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:48,120
Master, do you mean

17
00:02:48,480 --> 00:02:50,010
you are willing to teach me?

18
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:52,480
Although you are usually noisy,

19
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:54,060
you have a pure nature.

20
00:02:57,680 --> 00:02:59,940
You have some affinity for cultivation.

21
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,770
If you really want to learn,

22
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:03,140
I can teach you.

23
00:03:06,920 --> 00:03:08,680
Thank you, Master.

24
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,280
Rise.

25
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:20,160
I don't know when Tu Luohua will arrive.

26
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:21,840
Let me teach you how to practice magic first.

27
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:22,900
Thank you, Master.

28
00:03:23,440 --> 00:03:24,500
Thank you, Master.

29
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:26,640
Fufu, go find some arrows.

30
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:27,730
Go find some arrows.

31
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:32,060
Right away.

32
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:11,600
Miss Gesang.

33
00:04:15,440 --> 00:04:16,440
Don't be nervous.

34
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:17,959
Let's chat.

35
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:19,959
Lord Hu.

36
00:04:21,279 --> 00:04:22,200
Talk about what?

37
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:23,680
Miss Gesang, you are

38
00:04:24,640 --> 00:04:25,370
a tree demon.

39
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:27,800
What?

40
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:30,090
Are you going to kill me?

41
00:04:30,200 --> 00:04:31,460
Though you are a demon,

42
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:33,400
you have no hostility in you.

43
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:36,000
This means you've never killed anyone.

44
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:37,840
So I won't do anything to you.

45
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:40,060
No need to be so nervous around me.

46
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:44,680
Then what do you want from me?

47
00:04:46,320 --> 00:04:47,520
I just want to tell you

48
00:04:48,159 --> 00:04:50,690
not to have any wicked thoughts about Zuzong.

49
00:04:51,280 --> 00:04:54,000
If you make a mistake in the future,

50
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:59,280
I will definitely not spare you.

51
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,640
I only thought since he was a Golden Immortal,

52
00:05:51,640 --> 00:05:53,960
he must be different from ordinary mortals.

53
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:56,680
I just wanted him to transfer his divine power to me.

54
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:59,560
I would accept anyone, whether a pig or a dog.

55
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:04,160
I didn't even take a good look at his face.

56
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:06,200
Looking at him now,

57
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:09,360
even without an immortal body,

58
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:12,400
his upright posture

59
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:15,680
and refined demeanor

60
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:24,840
make him a supreme beauty in this world.

61
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:30,400
Sneaking around.

62
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:44,500
Brother Qingxuan.

63
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:47,760
I saw you standing here so tall and graceful,

64
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:49,720
alone in the empty corridor,

65
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,700
so I was afraid to disturb you.

66
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:56,200
Look,

67
00:06:56,960 --> 00:06:59,090
the spring scenery filling the garden

68
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:00,680
is quite beautiful.

69
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:04,560
Every flower, every blade of grass,

70
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:06,160
every terrace, every scene,

71
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:07,260
are all illusions.

72
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:12,400
It's not bad to have someone accompanying you

73
00:07:13,080 --> 00:07:14,740
in this bubble of an illusion.

74
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,000
Golden Immortal,

75
00:07:20,440 --> 00:07:23,040
are you from the heavens?

76
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:27,480
It depends on how you understand

77
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:30,040
the heavens.

78
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:36,640
My mother told me

79
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:40,170
that I am also a spirit branch that fell from the heavens.

80
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:45,280
Which heaven did you fall from?

81
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,760
How would I know?

82
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,400
It's just that,

83
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:52,880
as a tree,

84
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:54,480
you know,

85
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:58,960
we take root and sprout wherever we fall.

86
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:02,880
I am just one of thousands.

87
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:06,240
You are different from them.

88
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,040
Of course.

89
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:14,240
I'm so unique.

90
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:16,570
They have so many children,

91
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:20,040
some were cut down to be made into roof beams,

92
00:08:20,960 --> 00:08:23,080
some were so dull

93
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:26,880
that they are still a piece of broken wood after a hundred years.

94
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:29,280
Only I have the highest cultivation level.

95
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:31,480
Indeed.

96
00:08:32,640 --> 00:08:33,900
You are not that young.

97
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:37,200
You should have cultivated for over a thousand years,

98
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:37,880
or perhaps...

99
00:08:37,880 --> 00:08:38,880
Golden Immortal,

100
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,000
my age...

101
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:42,240
But you look very young,

102
00:08:43,760 --> 00:08:45,400
about fifteen or sixteen.

103
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:47,240
If you don't tell,

104
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,880
no one will know your real age.

105
00:08:52,560 --> 00:08:56,640
I didn't expect Brother Qingxuan with the eternal icy face

106
00:08:56,760 --> 00:08:58,840
to be such a kind person.

107
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:02,200
Handsome,

108
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:05,560
sweet-talking and kind-hearted.

109
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:09,560
Girls must all like you.

110
00:09:11,800 --> 00:09:14,000
This damn man is invulnerable,

111
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:15,610
impervious to everything,

112
00:09:15,640 --> 00:09:17,100
stubborn and unyielding.

113
00:09:25,280 --> 00:09:27,800
Master, Master, Master.

114
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:34,760
Hey.

115
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:38,680
Why panic?

116
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:46,890
Is there anything else?

117
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:50,360
What could I have?

118
00:09:50,680 --> 00:09:51,560
If you don't,

119
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:53,000
I do.

120
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:54,720
Hurry up and go.

121
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:02,600
Your power is weak,

122
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:04,260
and you don't know any spells.

123
00:10:04,640 --> 00:10:06,200
If you encounter monsters in the future,

124
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:07,520
just shout at this,

125
00:10:07,760 --> 00:10:08,820
"Sister, save me."

126
00:10:08,880 --> 00:10:09,740
And I will come.

127
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,400
Okay. Thank you.

128
00:10:25,760 --> 00:10:26,640
Gesang,

129
00:10:26,760 --> 00:10:28,160
you must also be careful.

130
00:10:28,160 --> 00:10:30,020
If you're in danger, just call for

131
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:31,800
Master.

132
00:10:32,640 --> 00:10:34,680
Just take care of yourself, rookie.

133
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:43,360
Master,

134
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:45,040
it's my first day of training.

135
00:10:45,040 --> 00:10:46,370
I'm still a bit nervous,

136
00:10:46,560 --> 00:10:47,760
but I'll do my best.

137
00:10:50,040 --> 00:10:51,240
Give me your hand.

138
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:55,080
You're going to hit me before we even start?

139
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:09,400
It's for you.

140
00:11:11,560 --> 00:11:12,480
For me?

141
00:11:13,280 --> 00:11:14,480
You have a mortal body

142
00:11:14,640 --> 00:11:15,840
with no cultivation.

143
00:11:17,040 --> 00:11:18,700
This ring can serve as a medium

144
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:21,810
to help you draw spiritual energy into your body.

145
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:25,440
You have an excellent innate bone structure.

146
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:27,570
If you temper it with spiritual energy

147
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:29,290
and cultivate diligently,

148
00:11:29,360 --> 00:11:30,820
your future achievements

149
00:11:30,880 --> 00:11:31,940
will be limitless.

150
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:37,240
Thank you, Master, for not despising my mortal dullness.

151
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:38,200
Put it on.

152
00:12:07,480 --> 00:12:08,600
Master, I got it.

153
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:12,700
I will definitely work harder in the future.

154
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:16,240
This ring

155
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:19,240
can only help you absorb spiritual energy.

156
00:12:19,760 --> 00:12:21,290
You have a unique physique.

157
00:12:22,160 --> 00:12:24,720
Converting spiritual energy into magic power

158
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:26,280
shouldn't be difficult for you.

159
00:12:26,280 --> 00:12:27,880
Practice more in the future.

160
00:12:28,160 --> 00:12:30,360
Never forget your original intention.

161
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:31,160
Yes.

162
00:12:32,760 --> 00:12:34,680
Immortal!

163
00:12:37,640 --> 00:12:38,440
Immortal!

164
00:12:38,680 --> 00:12:39,680
Is everything ready?

165
00:12:39,680 --> 00:12:40,760
To answer the Immortal,

166
00:12:40,760 --> 00:12:43,120
everything is ready in the main hall.

167
00:13:48,400 --> 00:13:48,720
Qiang Haihui.

168
00:13:48,720 --> 00:13:49,400
Jie Qianghaihui.

169
00:13:49,400 --> 00:13:49,560
Ping Jieqiang.
